    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i just don't get why it's so big of a deal. i've had juice with my meds before and felt totally fine. sounds like a bit of an exaggeration to say i have to avoid it entirely just for one glass. is there like a specific amount that is actually safe? like if i just have a small splash in my water or something it wouldn't matter, right?",
